{"tid":818060,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓仔好似扭親手","createTime":"2018-09-13T23:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T00:04:29.000Z","uid":43738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10d30fb230edebb9f66a03b8b8342a701e18eee8","tid":818060,"uid":43738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T23:48:00.000Z","msg":"有冇人去過何文田/旺角區有寵物診所係唔差 <br />\n我上網搵間間都講到黑店咁 想搵間正正常常 <br />\n我隻貓仔唔知咩事 可能玩個時扭親隻手 吊下吊下咁行 <br />\n但佢仲伸到爪磨爪又用到啲啲力咁  㩒落去又無話特別好痛叫 佢又有精神係度跳黎跳去  但明明隻手吊住咁行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係想帶去睇一睇醫生 唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4314a19b3cd6411bb0bf00172f068664d86d5c6d","tid":818060,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T23:52:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39965e6cc889c34ad2baf3cfe09e0abf723f969b","tid":818060,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T23:59:36.000Z","msg":"手同前足都唔識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a375a440bf5ad97120a022612fcb16abe3b0c314","tid":818060,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"39965e6cc889c34ad2baf3cfe09e0abf723f969b","tid":818060,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T23:59:36.000Z","msg":"手同前足都唔識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"前足唔係手？"},{"pid":"9bfd8142092d9c8fe3c35f38e6f2891d8e6d47d6","tid":818060,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>手同前足都唔識分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前足唔係手？</blockquote><br />\n叫開手手、腳腳。<br />\n<br />\n有時會叫前腳、後腳"}]}